---
source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
assertion_line: 249
info: css/escaped-attribute/test.css
---

# Input

```css
div span[foo="bar short\
short"] {
  color: red;
}

/* Should not break before `span`, since it doesn't reach printWidth */
div span[foo="bar long long long\
long long long long long long long long long long long long"] {
  color: red;
}

div {
  & span[foo="bar short\
short"] {
    color: red;
  }

  /* Should not break before `span`, since it doesn't reach printWidth */
  & span[foo="bar long long long\
long long long long long long long long long long long long"] {
    color: red;
  }
}

```


